    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is ideal for a dedicated project or as a parts car. The engine currently requires a major overhaul to be roadworthy, and there are significant rust spots along the wheel wells and undercarriage. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears, and the electronics are inconsistent. While it has a clean title, it will need a trailer for transport and substantial work to return to its former glory.",
